video_title: Top 5 Signs You Need Stronger Boundaries
transcript:
I'm Dr Julie and here's my top five
signs that you need to work on having
stronger boundaries number five you
often say yes when you want or need to
say no number four you hate letting
people down it just eats you up inside
when it feels like you have number three
you give so much of yourself in
relationships that you just feel drained
most of the time number two you over
share personal information and then
later on feel embarrassed or regret
doing it and number one you've been
putting everybody else's wants before
your own for so long you just don't
really know who you are anymore
